             was indicted for <rs id="t18151025-110-off649" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18151025-110-off649" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18151025-110-off649" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t18151025-110-victim949" type="victimName">
                        George 
                        Hagan
                     <interp inst="t18151025-110-victim949" type="surname" value="Hagan"></interp>
