                        <interp inst="t18151025-110-victim949" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , in the night time, of the <rs id="t18151025-110-cd650" type="crimeDate">12th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18151025-110-off649 t18151025-110-cd650"></join>, and burglariously stealing therein, five bushels of flour, value 3 l. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18151025-110-person950">
                        George 
                        Hagan
                     <interp inst="t18151025-110-person950" type="surname" value="Hagan"></interp>
